message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.AI, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with image quality assessment using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The application domain is medical imaging (cs.MED), and the paper uses semi-supervised learning techniques (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NEURON) to achieve its results.
